00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 9 =

20
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:16,740
Xinhe.

21
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:17,940
Your Majesty.

22
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:19,660
Xinhe.

23
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:21,900
I’m thirsty. Is there tea?

24
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:22,540
Your Majesty.

25
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:30,580
I just made this

26
00:02:30,660 --> 00:02:31,700
and haven’t drunk it.

27
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:37,300
Is there more?

28
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:47,060
Your Majesty, this isn’t hot enough.

29
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:48,780
It’s OK. Warm water will do.

30
00:02:54,380 --> 00:02:56,060
How come you’re so thirsty?

31
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,140
Give me.

32
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:09,940
I glanced at Liaozi several times

33
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:10,940
but he failed to pick up my hint.

34
00:03:11,980 --> 00:03:13,060
Ren Shouzhong was there, too.

35
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:15,740
If I made it too obvious, he’d be punished.

36
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:16,980
That was unnecessary.

37
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:19,060
You’re always so kind.

38
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,420
Actually,

39
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:24,020
it wasn’t his fault.

40
00:03:24,380 --> 00:03:26,620
Even I almost fell asleep

41
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,780
when Lv Yijian, Wang Zeng

42
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,500
and Li Di were debating back and forth.

43
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,620
Were there a straw,

44
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,260
I’d break it into two to hold my eyes lids.

45
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,700
Liaozi and the others stood there for six hours.

46
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:36,780
He must’ve been

47
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:38,260
battling sleepiness wholeheartedly

48
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:40,500
that he failed to read my eyes.

49
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,820
Totally understandable.

50
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:44,620
What exactly

51
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:45,980
was the debate about?

52
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,140
Were they lecturing you again?

53
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:52,460
Nothing important.

54
00:03:53,340 --> 00:03:54,300
They all had

55
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:55,460
their own opinions

56
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:58,460
and believed they were most loyal and honest.

57
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:59,860
They couldn’t convince each other.

58
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:07,100
Who do you think is right?

59
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,740
It’s easy to tell sometimes,

60
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:13,740
but not very often.

61
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:17,780
But they have the right to speak.

62
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:23,380
What’s this?

63
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,980
Will you marry me?

64
00:04:36,900 --> 00:04:37,820
Will you be with me

65
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,980
forever and ever?

66
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,260
Even if I’ll serve as a foil,

67
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:02,300
even if you don’t know me at all,

68
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:06,140
you only choose me for my family background

69
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,020
and Uncle Xue’s recommendation,

70
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:13,020
but I’ll finally

71
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:16,660
be able to see you more often.

72
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:01,460
You’re back.

73
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:02,540
Have a seat.

74
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,300
Tell me

75
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:06,540
how is Danshu doing in the palace?

76
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:08,900
Over the past few days,

77
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:11,060
she hasn’t met His Majesty once.

78
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:15,180
But according to my knowledge,

79
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,900
girls who entered the palace

80
00:06:16,900 --> 00:06:18,220
simultaneously

81
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,780
didn’t have the chance either.

82
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,700
= Chen Xichun =

83
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,620
Who will you choose to be the Empress?

84
00:06:37,420 --> 00:06:38,300
I guess

85
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:41,660
someone who fits this place

86
00:06:43,260 --> 00:06:44,060
and is able

87
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:47,220
to stay here

88
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:48,340
for the rest of her life.

89
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:56,580
Your Majesty.

90
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:02,020
Who exactly is the ruler of this world?

91
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:06,620
Places I’ve visited,

92
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,540
and things I’ve seen throughout my life

93
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:12,460
are nothing compared with her.

94
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:37,980
Minister will be buried in the imperial mausoleum.

95
00:08:38,700 --> 00:08:41,420
Cao Bin’s granddaughter is from a noble family

96
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:45,140
who’s well-educated and mannered.

97
00:08:45,380 --> 00:08:50,020
Emperor and empress rule the world as a whole.

98
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:54,940
Consultants are needed for internal affairs.

99
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:57,500
Following traditions,

100
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:02,180
Assistant Minister,

101
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:04,020
Minister of Personnel

102
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:07,100
and Consultant of the Cabinet

103
00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:10,940
and Ministry of Supervision Lv Yijian

104
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:13,780
are sent to conduct the formality.

105
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,900
Envoys made the announcement

106
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:19,460
and asked about the family background.

107
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:21,260
Danshu is

108
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,140
Mr. Cao Qi and his wife’s daughter,

109
00:09:24,700 --> 00:09:27,020
and the late minister,

110
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:29,300
Duke Ji, Cao Bin’s granddaughter.

111
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:41,220
= 1034 A.D. =

112
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:02,580
Heng, is your marriage with Su Zimei

113
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,580
as happy as you expected?

114
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:07,900
I didn’t expect anything

115
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:10,940
but simply follow my parents’ order.

116
00:10:12,380 --> 00:10:14,780
Is it the same as you imagined?

117
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:17,060
We’ve known each other like forever.

118
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,060
What could be different?

119
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:23,740
Well, he’s the one.

120
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:29,300
But he can be surprisingly childish.

121
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:32,300
Sometimes, he acts like a kid.

122
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:35,380
When he’s satisfied with his own works,

123
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,540
he doesn’t show them to me directly,

124
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,900
but always puts them

125
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:42,460
next to things I usually use.

126
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,060
He wrote them for you, didn’t he?

127
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:50,140
Heng,

128
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:52,700
that’s what a perfect marriage should be.

129
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:57,780
Yours is perfect.

130
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:01,180
You know what,

131
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:03,420
when I heard you were chosen,

132
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:05,100
I wasn’t surprised at all.

133
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:05,980
It was only natural.

134
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:09,180
With your look and talent,

135
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:10,500
only you

136
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:11,900
deserve such a marriage.

137
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:14,020
You said

138
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:16,060
you shot the wild goose yourself.

139
00:11:16,540 --> 00:11:17,860
Nobody would marry you.

140
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:21,900
But look, he offered you jade

141
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:24,180
to marry you.

142
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:45,460
Your Majesty.

143
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,540
We’re only going to have breakfast.

144
00:11:52,940 --> 00:11:54,140
Why are you dressed up like this?

145
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:56,620
= Madam Yu =
Betrothal presents

146
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:58,100
will be given to the Empress today.

147
00:11:58,300 --> 00:12:00,220
We’re here to congratulate you.

148
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,260
It’s a big day.

149
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:02,540
We can’t dress too casually.

150
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,860
May you and the Empress

151
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:08,140
enjoy a happy marriage

152
00:12:08,180 --> 00:12:10,220
and longevity with more children to come.

153
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,740
Good. Thanks.

154
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:16,780
You’re considerate.

155
00:12:17,180 --> 00:12:18,340
With you sharing the Empress’ burden,

156
00:12:18,860 --> 00:12:20,500
both our family and state will prosper.

157
00:12:21,860 --> 00:12:22,860
Right now,

158
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:25,380
I’ll toast you with porridge

159
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,500
to thank you for your blessings.

160
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,900
Follow the rules.

161
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:59,580
Bow again.

162
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:01,380
Confer the title of the Empress

163
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:04,940
on Minister and Duke Cao Bin’s granddaughter.

164
00:13:05,260 --> 00:13:08,780
Rites shall be performed accordingly.

165
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,060
Mr. Yan

166
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,220
is living a carefree life.

167
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:56,100
He’s written several poems.

168
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:59,300
It’s said he has a new singer.

169
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,500
Whenever he composes verses,

170
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:02,180
he’ll invite friends over to drink

171
00:14:02,180 --> 00:14:03,060
and have her sing, too.

172
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:06,660
His wife isn’t too happy though.

173
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:43,620
Seal Carrier Li Di,

174
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,420
Deputy Carrier Wang Sui,

175
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:50,140
are here to deliver the Empress’ Seal.

176
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:57,940
Poems written by scholars who passed the exam

177
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,660
are prone to be flamboyant.

178
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:02,100
Those who adopt unadorned

179
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,940
and more traditional styles are hardly admitted.

180
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:09,540
Mr. Yan suggested the exam system

181
00:15:10,060 --> 00:15:11,380
should be upgraded years ago.

182
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:14,220
Fan Zhongyan supported it

183
00:15:14,220 --> 00:15:15,940
with sharp and solid reasons.

184
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:19,460
Sadly, I wasn’t in charge back then,

185
00:15:20,220 --> 00:15:21,620
so I could only agree to it in silence.

186
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:28,620
I’ll tell the Ministry of Rites

187
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:30,940
that word usage is not only one criterion.

188
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:33,220
The angle, organization and reasoning

189
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,140
are equally important.

190
00:15:52,460 --> 00:15:54,980
Announcement of conferring:

191
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:59,460
On the third day

192
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:02,140
of November

193
00:16:02,580 --> 00:16:04,380
1034 A.D.,

194
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:09,620
His Majesty announces that heaven and earth...

195
00:16:11,460 --> 00:16:12,300
Your Majesty.

196
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:14,340
It’s about time.

197
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:15,780
Please get changed.

198
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:27,620
Alright.

199
00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:38,660
Empress shall be diligent and disciplined,

200
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:43,140
respect ancestors and be a role model

201
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:45,700
to contribute to the prosperity of the state.

202
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,100
That will be ideal.

203
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:34,980
Your Majesty’s marriage will shape the order.

204
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:39,780
The state will be in harmony and everlasting.

205
00:18:40,700 --> 00:18:45,020
The state will be in harmony and everlasting.

206
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:43,900
Ma’am,

207
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:47,740
people in Huaizhou are suffering a lot lately.

208
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:51,020
There are emergency reports every day.

209
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:55,100
His Majesty must be caught up with work.

210
00:19:56,540 --> 00:20:00,460
= Deng Baoji =

211
00:20:01,060 --> 00:20:03,060
I’ll have servants check it.

212
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:13,380
Huaizhou is heavily struck.

213
00:20:15,100 --> 00:20:16,580
I heard from my father and brother

214
00:20:18,700 --> 00:20:20,020
that the locals

215
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:21,380
have been foodless for days.

216
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:27,780
Fan Zhongyan there wrote proposals to His Majesty

217
00:20:27,780 --> 00:20:28,940
stressing the urgency.

218
00:20:29,780 --> 00:20:30,820
“Your Majesty, imagine what will happen

219
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:32,780
if the palace is lack of food for only half a day”.

220
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,540
His Majesty is benevolent.

221
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:38,020
He must be under great pressure.

222
00:20:42,580 --> 00:20:43,780
This matter is the priority.

223
00:20:45,380 --> 00:20:46,820
Don’t distract His Majesty.

224
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:52,100
You’re considerate.

225
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:04,820
During today’s banquet,

226
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:07,260
Prime Minister Lv, Li and Wang,

227
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,620
Chief Li and Wang

228
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:09,700
were in an excellent mood.

229
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:11,620
They even wrote poems and recalled the past.

230
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,420
None of them

231
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:14,860
were as hostile as before

232
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:16,620
in or out of court.

233
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:20,380
The woman they unanimously chose

234
00:21:20,380 --> 00:21:21,540
became the Empress.

235
00:21:22,260 --> 00:21:23,620
Of course they were happy

236
00:21:24,460 --> 00:21:26,020
and had nothing to argue.

237
00:21:29,940 --> 00:21:30,740
Besides,

238
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:32,500
Mr. Xue was a little bit drunk.

239
00:21:32,780 --> 00:21:34,180
He asked Mr. Li

240
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,900
if he was close to Ouyang Xiu.

241
00:21:36,340 --> 00:21:36,980
He heard

242
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:39,060
Ouyang Xiu’s wife Xu passed away

243
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:40,940
and intended to marry his fourth daughter

244
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:41,700
to him.

245
00:21:45,380 --> 00:21:48,420
After Xue Kui’s third daughter died in labor,

246
00:21:48,820 --> 00:21:50,180
he married the fifth one

247
00:21:50,180 --> 00:21:51,340
to Wang Gongchen.

248
00:21:52,540 --> 00:21:54,860
When I heard that from Han Qi, I thought

249
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:57,620
if Wang Gongchen and his wife

250
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,340
were deeply in love,

251
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:00,820
how devastated would he be

252
00:22:01,020 --> 00:22:02,820
after losing her.

253
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:05,420
He wouldn’t have the mood to remarry so soon.

254
00:22:06,740 --> 00:22:07,980
If they weren’t close,

255
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:10,340
wouldn’t he hold a grudge against the Xues

256
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:11,900
and mistreat

257
00:22:12,300 --> 00:22:14,020
another Xue girl?

258
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:18,260
Now, he wants to marry his fourth daughter

259
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:20,500
to Ouyang Xiu right after his wife passed away.

260
00:22:23,660 --> 00:22:25,700
They all treat their daughters the same.

261
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,020
If they can marry men

262
00:22:28,420 --> 00:22:30,260
who are capable and promising,

263
00:22:30,260 --> 00:22:31,340
that’ll be good marriages.

264
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:32,740
Similarly, when they chose the Empress,

265
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:33,820
they wouldn’t care

266
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,260
about my preference.

267
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:40,620
You clearly love Miss Chen.

268
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:44,260
Actually...actually, you can

269
00:22:44,460 --> 00:22:45,540
have her back later.

270
00:22:46,100 --> 00:22:47,500
Even if she can’t be the Empress,

271
00:22:47,860 --> 00:22:48,860
she can still stay with you

272
00:22:48,980 --> 00:22:50,140
as a concubine.

273
00:22:52,660 --> 00:22:54,060
She was carefully chosen

274
00:22:54,060 --> 00:22:55,300
for me

275
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:57,460
for a reason.

276
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:01,020
Commoners have wild fantasies

277
00:23:01,580 --> 00:23:03,700
about life in the palace.

278
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:05,100
They don’t know how hard it is.

279
00:23:06,020 --> 00:23:06,780
It’s possible

280
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,740
that they’ll cross the line.

281
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:11,620
Once that happens,

282
00:23:12,820 --> 00:23:14,220
who will suffer?

283
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:19,420
Officials had their reasons

284
00:23:19,420 --> 00:23:21,220
to have one from the prominent family

285
00:23:21,580 --> 00:23:22,820
be the Empress.

286
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,340
I didn’t understand it when I was little,

287
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:26,540
but I do now.

288
00:23:29,100 --> 00:23:30,340
Those officials

289
00:23:30,340 --> 00:23:31,380
are funny.

290
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:33,220
They can be both rigid

291
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:35,740
and flexible.

292
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:38,740
Speaking of the Empress,

293
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:41,380
her family is noble,

294
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:45,340
yet she is well-versed in riding and archery.

295
00:23:45,780 --> 00:23:46,700
She used to dress as a boy

296
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:48,340
to go hunting with her brothers a lot.

297
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:50,540
Also, she wore men’s outfits

298
00:23:50,540 --> 00:23:52,020
to listen to Fan Zhongyan’s lectures

299
00:23:52,100 --> 00:23:53,620
at Nanjing Academy.

300
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:56,300
How come those behaviors

301
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:57,540
weren’t considered as misconduct?

302
00:23:57,900 --> 00:23:59,380
How ironic!

303
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:06,980
Your Majesty.

304
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,140
I was also invited

305
00:24:09,140 --> 00:24:10,100
to drink with them.

306
00:24:10,500 --> 00:24:11,500
I’m sorry

307
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:12,660
that I overstepped my bounds.

308
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:18,060
They were afraid

309
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:20,100
if I married the girl I like,

310
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:21,700
I’d love her too much.

311
00:24:25,100 --> 00:24:26,460
Cao is from a good family.

312
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:27,700
She’s an all-round talent

313
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,740
but so plain-looking

314
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:32,100
that her ex-husband jumped out of the window

315
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:34,020
on their wedding night.

316
00:24:34,620 --> 00:24:35,700
Such an empress

317
00:24:35,780 --> 00:24:37,300
would never distract the Emperor

318
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:40,020
from his work.

319
00:24:40,180 --> 00:24:40,780
Actually,

320
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:46,780
well, rumors may not be true.

321
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:48,660
It’s impossible

322
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:49,940
for officials

323
00:24:49,980 --> 00:24:51,540
to meet unmarried girls.

324
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:55,860
I don’t care

325
00:24:55,860 --> 00:24:56,700
about her look.

326
00:24:56,700 --> 00:24:58,100
Her appearance doesn’t matter.

327
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:00,780
Since she’s the chosen one,

328
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:01,700
as the Emperor,

329
00:25:02,060 --> 00:25:02,900
I have to accept

330
00:25:02,900 --> 00:25:04,180
the right choice.

331
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:11,300
Maoze,

332
00:25:13,300 --> 00:25:15,220
I can’t be in the same room

333
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:17,060
with my perfect wife right now.

334
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,580
I’m tired and suffocated.

335
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:24,420
It’s snowing heavily.

336
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:27,060
I’d like to take a walk in the plum garden.

337
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:30,740
Tell the Empress...

338
00:25:34,780 --> 00:25:36,500
Make up a convincing excuse

339
00:25:37,260 --> 00:25:38,500
and tell her to eat without me.

340
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,100
Don’t wait up.

341
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:44,940
Yes.

342
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:34,380
Your Majesty...

343
00:26:37,780 --> 00:26:38,620
Maoze,

344
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:42,420
is His Majesty still busy

345
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:44,140
processing reports from Huaizhou?

346
00:26:44,620 --> 00:26:46,300
= Zhang Maoze, courtesy name Pingfu =

347
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:05,460
Ma’am.

348
00:27:06,100 --> 00:27:06,740
Your Majesty...

349
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,940
Your Majesty is busy

350
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:11,260
with state affairs.

351
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:13,780
I understand.

352
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:21,940
Mr. Zhang, Mr. Deng,

353
00:27:23,540 --> 00:27:25,020
please go to the kitchen

354
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:27,340
to heat a few light flavored dishes

355
00:27:28,380 --> 00:27:29,900
and take them to His Majesty’s chamber.

356
00:27:35,380 --> 00:27:36,300
I’m tired.

357
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:39,700
I’m going to bed.

358
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:19,620
I’ll kill you!

359
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:22,500
You’re dead. Go die!

360
00:28:24,340 --> 00:28:25,220
Go die!

361
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:27,580
You’re bad!

362
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:33,060
You’re bad

363
00:28:33,860 --> 00:28:34,460
Go die!

364
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:36,900
You’re so bad! I’ll kill you!

365
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:39,260
Go die!

366
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:43,020
You’re bad!

367
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,380
You’re bad!

368
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:54,820
What’s wrong, young lady?

369
00:28:56,340 --> 00:28:58,020
It killed my rabbit.

370
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:01,780
I did a lot of work for Instructor Jia

371
00:29:02,100 --> 00:29:03,620
and separated tons of strings

372
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:06,140
to get the rabbit.

373
00:29:08,220 --> 00:29:10,820
She was this big and white as snow.

374
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:12,540
So cute.

375
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:14,700
When I fed her fresh vegetables,

376
00:29:15,260 --> 00:29:17,540
she’d chew them happily.

377
00:29:18,580 --> 00:29:19,940
Her eyes were red,

378
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:21,820
lips were pink.

379
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:25,580
Go die!

380
00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:27,220
It already died.

381
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:29,340
Why are you still torturing it?

382
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:32,100
= Zhang Bihan =
It killed my rabbit.

383
00:29:32,100 --> 00:29:32,860
I have to

384
00:29:32,860 --> 00:29:34,460
avenge her death.

385
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:36,820
My rabbit was so nice.

386
00:29:37,060 --> 00:29:38,420
She must be in a lot of pain

387
00:29:38,420 --> 00:29:39,700
