439
00:33:17,660 --> 00:33:19,100
at the Great Xiangguo market

440
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:20,180
made by Mr. Cui.

441
00:33:20,860 --> 00:33:21,540
That day,

442
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:23,780
you told me that

443
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:26,020
to thank me

444
00:33:26,780 --> 00:33:27,820
